              <h3>Baltal Valley</h3>
              <p>
                  Baltal is a magnificent valley located at the foot of Zoji La, along the banks of Sindh's cheerfully running river. The scenic valley, located 15 kilometers from Sonamarg, is vital because it gives a shorter route to the famous Amarnath Cave.
